# symbols

**Instance Property**

A view that provides child views that you can use in the drawing callback.

## Declaration

```swift
var symbols: Symbols
```

## Discussion

Uniquely tag each child view using the `View/tag(_:)` modifier, so that you can find them from within your renderer using the [doc://com.apple.SwiftUI/documentation/SwiftUI/GraphicsContext/resolveSymbol(id:)] method.
